sequenceDiagram
  participant Browser
  participant API as Regional API Gateway
  participant Lambda as Regional API Lambda
  participant DB as Regional DynamoDB
  participant Publisher as Regional Outbox Publisher
  participant Queue as Regional SQS
  participant Worker as Regional Worker
  Browser->>API: Authenticated request + idempotency key
  API->>Lambda: Invoke
  Lambda->>DB: Transaction: business item + outbox
  DB-->>Lambda: Committed
  Lambda-->>Browser: 202 Accepted
  Publisher->>DB: Claim pending event
  Publisher->>Queue: Publish job
  Publisher->>DB: Mark delivered
  Queue->>Worker: Deliver job
  Worker->>DB: Claim lease and persist result
